         <abstract>
            <p>If only to combat the dehumanizing effects of bigness, big business has to take positive steps to be a good neighbor in the communities where it operates. Business has a responsibility, not merely to obey the law, but to take the initiative in experimenting with new solutions to social problems.</p>
